      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANDIT DARYL (4) is on a hot streak of form, the latest charging out of the boxes early and scoring at Gawler (37.24), making it five straight wins. Hard to fault recent form and looks a key chance again. URANA SPACE (8) copped a check in the run and finished fourth (38.04) in a Grade 5/6 at Gawler over 643m. Does go very well at this course. May be worth another try. BACARDI GIRL (1) was prominent throughout when an impressive winner two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 6th and beaten 10 lengths at Sandown (43.14). The form from her last run stacks up well. Bold showing expected. ADHANA MADI (5) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
